  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db0\u0db8\u0dca\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dd6\u0d9a\u0da9\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A puppet of Dhammika Perera Basil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Samagi Jana Balawega MP Naleen Bandara said that no matter what agendas Minister Dhammika Perera has, he is currently working as a puppet of former Minister Basil Rajapaksa.",
        "He said this while attending a press conference held today (07th) at the office of the opposition leader in Colombo.",
        "Meanwhile, Member of Parliament Naleen Bandara stated that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa is using the repression to the maximum extent for his own safety.",
        "These days Gotabhaya Rajapaksa are using suppression to the maximum for their own safety. We saw that on many occasions yesterday. I also had to face one situation. Yesterday, we filed a case of maximization on behalf of the entire farming population of this country, demanding compensation for 936,000 farmers during the high season. The government has taken approval from the cabinet. Nearly 936,000 families have been identified. It has been decided to pay them 41 billion rupees. We filed a case to pay that amount to those families. After making a silent protest, he came to the President's House to tell the reason for that silent protest. How were our farmers treated there? These farmers were watered. Also, Sri Lanka was tear gassed the most times yesterday. They were tear gassed 4 times. That hit is not only for farmers. People walking on the road were also beaten. So it is the police who don't know how to use tear gas that have been appointed as Gotabaya Rajapaksa's guards today.",
        "If anyone thinks that this country can be rebuilt within a mechanism with Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, it will never happen. Two of our friends also thought so. Gota is said to be a failure, but our good friend. Harin Mitra also said about Gota's curse. But today they too have fallen into the same trap after thinking that they can fix this by staying with Fail Gotabhaya.",
        "Who did Dhammika Perera come to Parliament for? For Basil. Basil did not quit, he retreated. Basil Rajapaksa made a strategic retreat. Now again a large public protest has been directed at the government. What are you going to do to stop it now? Previously, we put Ranil Wickramasinghe out of those houses to suppress the public protest. At that time, when he was about to attack, Udaviya Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was hiding in the bunkers, got out of the iron and escaped. Now it's time to hit that iron. Now Ranil Wickramasinghe is thrown out again and another formula is being tried. Dhammika Perera was brought to its master plan. Therefore, Dhammika Perera is a puppet of Basil Rajapaksa. Dhammis have separate agendas. But today he is working as a puppet of Basil Rajapaksa, he said."
      ],
